Lovina Onyegbule bụ onye Naijirịa na-eme egwuregwu.
Onyegbule nwere nsogbu ịhụ ụzọ ma na-asọmpi na agbụrụ T11 na F11
Ọ gụrụ ṅkwukọrịta na Our Saviour Institute of Science and Technology
O sonyere na 2015 African Games, ebe o ritere ihe ṅrite ọla edo na 100m T11 na 200m T11 ihe omume, na 2016 Paralympics.
